flowchart LR
    STORE[Secrets Store\nVault / KMS]

    STORE --> INJECT[inject at boot\nenv / sidecar]
    INJECT --> SVC[Service Runtime]
    SVC --> USE[use secret]

    STORE --> SCHED[rotation scheduler]
    SCHED --> NEWV[generate new version]
    NEWV --> GRACE[dual-version grace period]
    GRACE --> REVOKE[revoke old version]
    REVOKE --> AUDIT[audit: rotation event]

    STORE --> DETECT[leak detection]
    DETECT --> ALERT[alert + emergency revoke]
